data.description: Price Improvement! Looking for an affordable home in Edmond schools, look no further! Homes in this small tight knit neighborhood don't come up for sale often. It is centrally located in the heart of Edmond close to schools, shopping, restaurants, Quail Springs Mall, Chisholm Creek, and anything else you need. It has new carpets throughout and is ready for its new owners! It also has a NEW ROOF! Do you need space? This home has it. It boasts 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms with 2 living areas, a formal dining room and an eat in kitchen! The main bedroom is large with a huge walk in closet. The two additional bedrooms are also good sized with big closets and a jack and jill bathroom between them. Out back you'll find a patio to enjoy the evening and watch the sun set. This home has a HUGE yard and sits on a corner lot. The neighborhood also has a large park and playground for you to enjoy. Come check it out today! Seller offering a home warranty for the buyer! The seller is motivated!
